---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Frequently Asked Questions | Romillie Hadeljo">
  <div class="bg-emerald-950 min-h-screen text-stone-200">
    <main class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-white mb-8 border-b border-white/10 pb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        
        <p class="text-emerald-200/60 mb-12 text-lg">Everything you need to know about your stay at Romillie Hadeljo.</p>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Arrival, Departure & Check-In -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Arrival, Departure & Check-In</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-sm">
                <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">What are the check-in and check-out times?</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">Check-in is from 2:00 PM onwards, and check-out is by 11:00 AM. If you require early check-in or late check-out, please let us know in advance, and we will do our best to accommodate you based on availability.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-sm">
                <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">How do check-in and key pickup work?</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">Upon arrival, the Host or Caretaker will personally greet you and help you check in. Keys can be collected and deposited through our building staff. Please note that self check-in via smart door is not available.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-sm">
                <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Do you offer luggage storage?</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">Yes, we can securely store your luggage if you arrive before check-in or wish to explore the city after checking out.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- Guest Policies -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Guest Policies</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-sm">
                <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">What are the guest eligibility and ID requirements?</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">The primary guest must be at least 18 years old. We accept Passports, Aadhaar Cards, and Driving Licenses as valid ID proofs. Local IDs are also allowed.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-sm">
                <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Are unmarried couples or all-male groups allowed?</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">Groups with only male guests are allowed at the property. However, unmarried couples are strictly not allowed to stay.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-sm">
                <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Is smoking or alcohol consumption allowed?</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">No. Both smoking and alcohol consumption are strictly prohibited anywhere within the property premises (indoors and outdoors).</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-sm">
                <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Is the property wheelchair accessible?</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">No, this property is not accessible to guests who use a wheelchair. Please make travel arrangements accordingly.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- General Amenities -->
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Amenities & Services</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-sm">
                <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Is breakfast included?</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">Yes, a complimentary breakfast is served daily for all our guests in the dining area. Guests can also enjoy homemade meals prepared by our onsite cook upon request.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-sm">
                <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Do you have on-site parking?</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">Yes, we provide free private parking for our guests. No prior reservation for parking is required.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-sm">
                <h3 class="text-white font-medium mb-2">Is there Wi-Fi available?</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">High-speed Wi-Fi is available throughout the property, including all guest rooms and common areas, free of charge.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 p-8 bg-emerald-900/30 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-sm text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-white mb-4">Still have questions?</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-300 mb-6">We're here to help you plan your perfect stay.</p>
          <a href="/#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-emerald-950 px-8 py-3 rounded-sm font-medium hover:bg-stone-100 transition-colors">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
